title: 051 - Is Connor A Scumlord?
description: On today's show, the guys realize Connor may be a bigger scumbag than they thought, they go through some #PodFacts, and get into everything else on this feel good Friday. Don't forget to send your questions to @ThePodPMI on Instagram and Twitter. Be safe, and have a great weekend. Enjoy.
